xmon (1.5.6-1.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Change priority to optional to match the archive overrides file;
    pass -isp to dpkg-gencontrol to make lintian happy.
  * Remove the postinst and prerm which were only used to handle the /usr/doc
    symlink anymore.
  * Add a note in the manpage about xhost, xauth and security. (Closes: #78598)
  * Explicitly builddepend on libxaw7-dev. (Closes: #169985)
  * Save errno before calling perror, supposedly the latter is allowed to
    change the former. (Closes: #174792)

 -- Filip Van Raemdonck <mechanix@debian.org>  Thu, 02 Jan 2003 21:03:18 +0100

